lyrics:
[verse]
Everyday my heart longs for your touch
Can't seem to get enough, I'm in love so much
You're the light that guides me through
Baby, my love for you is eternally true

[chorus]
I'm so in love, so deep within
With you, my darling, it's where I begin
You're the rhythm of my heart, the melody in my soul
Forever and always, together we'll grow
